<!-- Main body
================== -->
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="section-header">
	  <div class="container">
	    <div class="row">
	      <div class="col-md-12">
		    <!-- Remove the .animated class if you don't want things to move -->
			<h1 class="animated slideInLeft"><span>Blog</span></h1>
		  </div>
		</div>
	  </div>
    </div>
	<div class="container">
	  <div class="row">

		<%  _.each(flash, function(message, type){ %>
			<div class="alert alert-<%= type %>"><%= message %></div>
		<% }); %>

	    <!-- Contact us form -->
		<div class="col-sm-6">
		  <h2 class="hl top-zero">Create Blog</h2>
		  <hr>
		
			<form role="form" action="/blog/create" method="POST">
			  <input name="id" type="hidden" value="<%= post.id %>" />
			  <div class="form-group">
				<label for="title">Title</label>
				<input type="text" class="form-control" id="title" placeholder="Enter title" value="<%= post.title %>" name="title" />
			  </div>
			  <div class="form-group">
				<label for="name">Blog</label>
				<textarea class="form-control" rows="20" name="body" placeholder="Enter blog"><%= post.body %></textarea>
			  </div>
			  <div class="form-group">
				<label for="tags">Tags</label>
				<input type="text" class="form-control" id="tags" value="<% if(post.tags){ %><%= post.tags %><% } %>" placeholder="Example : hvac, lennox, savings" name="tags" />
			  </div>
			  <div class="form-group">
				<label for="link">Link</label>
				<p>This allows you to edit the url of the blog.  Normally, you want to leave this empty.</p>
				<input type="text" class="form-control" id="link" value="<% if(post.link){ %><%= post.link %><% } %>" name="link" />
			  </div>			  
			  <input type='hidden' name='_csrf' value='<%= _csrf %>' />
			  <button type="submit" class="hl-btn hl-btn-green">Save</button>
			</form>
	
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-6">
			<br />
			<p>Markdown Syntax</p>
			<pre>
HEADERS 			

# H1
## H2
### H3
#### H4
##### H5
###### H6

EMPHASIS

Emphasis, aka italics, with *asterisks* or _underscores_.
Strong emphasis, aka bold, with **asterisks** or __underscores__.
Combined emphasis with **asterisks and _underscores_**.
Strikethrough uses two tildes. ~~Scratch this.~~

LISTS

1. First ordered list item
2. Another item

* Unordered list can use asterisks
- Or minuses
+ Or pluses

LINKS

[Link text](https://www.google.com)

IMAGES

(/path/to/img.jpg)
			</pre>
		</div>

	  </div>
	</div>
  </div>
